author: Pixeluchiha
text: I watched all their perspectives on 10 different devices because I don't want to miss any of them. I love all of them and I am glad they are happy and having fun! To both the girls and the fans, stay happy and enjoy yourselves, because you bring joy to people!

author: Johar Alif
text: @shinra i think  its destroy the purpose of the game

author: Pixeluchiha
text: I 1000% agree with you guys. I just really enjoy the conversations out of it. Also, I think I have awakened a clout chaser inside of me, and I will need to get it surgically removed. But what I say is true. I just don't know when to stop, and can't pick just one member to send it to.

author: YT C
text: @Pixeluchiha  glad to hear you realized about it, hope you can fix it later on

author: Pixeluchiha
text: @YT C  i do want to fix it, but at the same time, i dont. I realise that it isn't the best thing to do as a community member, but I enjoy doing it. I hope if I do it in the future, there will be more people like you to criticize me. I do need the critique.

author: shinra
text: @Pixeluchiha  it will come off to other people as a bit spammy but it's okay to comment, we won't hold you back for it. enjoy the streams of the girls!

author: Pixeluchiha
text: @shinra  I do agree it is spammy, but I tend to think of it as a hobby. I will continue to listen to feedback, both encouragement and criticism, and do what my gut tells me to. But if it becomes too much of a problem, I will calm it down, maybe change how I comment or something. Someone previously told me it looked like I wanted something in return, and it made me feel terrible that some people, and maybe even the girls, thought that way.
